# Navigation ( backward / forward ) C=ctrl, M=alt

  Character-wise                                  C-b , C-f
  Word-wise                                       M-b , M-f
  Line beginning / end                            C-a , C-e
  Delete word-wise                                C-w , M-d
  Delete line beginning / end                     C-u , C-k
  Reverse search history                          C-r
  Advance through history                         C-p , C-n
  Undo edit                                       C-_
  Revert to original                              M-r
